OL,3,CCardiff medical student undergoes
OL,4,Cquadruple amputation
OL,6,FA 23-year-old medical student from
OL,7,FCardiff University has undergone
OL,8,Fsurgery to shorten all four of her
OL,9,Flimbs, after a life threatening
OL,10,Finfection.
OL,12,FLily McGarry, was admitted to hospital
OL,13,Fin January 2025, with flu-like
OL,14,Fsymptoms, which rapidly worsened into
OL,15,Fseptic shock.
OL,17,FShe was diagnosed with meningococcal
OL,18,Fsepticaemia, a severe and aggressive
OL,19,Finfection.
