OL,3,CCardiff medical student undergoes
OL,4,Cquadruple amputation
OL,6,FWhilst being treated at the University
OL,7,FHospital in Wales, she suffered two
OL,8,Fcardiac arrests and spent two weeks in
OL,9,Fa coma.
OL,11,FThe infection caused severe blood flow
OL,12,Fissues, and resulted in Lily
OL,13,Fundergoing surgery to shorten all four
OL,14,Fof her limbs.
OL,16,FUndertaken by the Plastics Team at
OL,17,FMorriston Hospital in Swansea.
