OL,3,CCardiff medical student undergoes
OL,4,Cquadruple amputation
OL,6,FNow her family are campaigning to
OL,7,Fraise money for advanced prosthetics,
OL,8,Fso that Lily can return to the
OL,9,Factivities she loved.
OL,11,FBefore her illness, she was an avid
OL,12,Fswimmer, runner and surfer.
OL,14,FHer family hopes advanced prosthetics
OL,15,Fwill give her the mobility and
OL,16,Findependence to return to these
OL,17,Factivities.
