OL,6,FJust one prosthetic legs costs over
OL,7,F#100,000 and so far the family have
OL,8,Fraised over #170,000, with over 4000
OL,9,Fdonations.
OL,11,FThe family are also supporting the
OL,12,Fcharity Limb Power, which supports
OL,13,Findividuals with limb impairments
OL,14,Fthrough physical activities, sports
OL,15,Fand the arts.
